{"lemma":"سُخْنٍ","slug":"سُخْنٍ","root":"س.خ.ن","root_slug":"س-خ-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/س-خ-ن","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19242","","n19244","n19245","n19246"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8F%D8%AE%D9%92%D9%86%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be hot, to become hot"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be ill, to become ill"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to heat","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"hot"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"warm"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root س خ ن (s ḵ n). Compare Aramaic שחן."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19242","headword_ar":"سَخُنَ","root":"sxn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, S, MA, L, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxana","text_ar":"سَخَنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, MA, L, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TK;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxina","text_ar":"سَخِنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, Msb, K,) which is of the dial. of Benoo-'Ámir, (L,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TK;) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxuwnapN","text_ar":"سُخُونَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, S, MA, L, Msb, K,) which is of the first [agreeably with analogy] (JK, S, MA) and of the second also, (S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxonapN","text_ar":"سُخْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, L, K,) which is of the first, (JK,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxonN","text_ar":"سُخْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MA, L, K, [accord. to some copies of the K, in which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biDam~atayoni","text_ar":"بِضَمَّتَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is put instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biDam~ihin~a","text_ar":"بِضَمِّهِنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"after these three inf. ns.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxunN","text_ar":"سُخُنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) which is likewise of the first, (MA,) [or of the first and second,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxaAnapN","text_ar":"سَخَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, Msb, K,) [also of the first accord. to general analogy,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxanN","text_ar":"سَخَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) [which is of the third verb;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, hot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"warm;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, MA, L, K;) said of water, (JK, S, L, Msb,) &c. (S, MA, L, Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxanati Aln~aAru","text_ar":"سَخَنَتِ النَّارُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqidoru","text_ar":"القِدْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxunat","text_ar":"سَخُنَت"},{"kind":"text","text":",] aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxonN","text_ar":"سُخْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxuwnapN","text_ar":"سُخُونَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The fire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the cooking-pot, became hot."},{"kind":"text","text":"] (L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxunati AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"سَخُنَتِ الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxanat","text_ar":"سَخَنَت"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxinat","text_ar":"سَخِنَت"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ground became hot"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxunato Ealayohi Al$~amosu","text_ar":"سَخُنَتْ عَلَيْهِ الشَّمْسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sun became hot upon him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: in the dial. of Benoo-'Ámir"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxinato","text_ar":"سَخِنَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxuna Alyawomu","text_ar":"سَخُنَ اليَوْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxana","text_ar":"سَخَنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", and some say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxina","text_ar":"سَخِنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxonN","text_ar":"سُخْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxunN","text_ar":"سُخُنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The day was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, hot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"warm."},{"kind":"text","text":"] (L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxunati Ald~aAb~apu","text_ar":"سَخُنَتِ الدَّابَّةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The beast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"being made to run,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became hot in its bones, and light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agile, in its running;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or simply,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became hot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see EM pp. 172 and 173;)] as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxanat","text_ar":"سَخَنَت"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxinato Eayonuhu","text_ar":"سَخِنَتْ عَيْنُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr, (JK, * S, MA, L, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxunato","text_ar":"سَخُنَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, L,) or the former only, (L,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxonapN","text_ar":"سُخْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, * MA, L, K, [in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxonap","text_ar":"سَخْنَة"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxuwnN","text_ar":"سُخُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, L, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxanN","text_ar":"سَخَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K, [accord. to the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxonN","text_ar":"سَخْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this is a mistake,])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qar~ato","text_ar":"قَرَّتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * L, K *) [i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His eye was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, hot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inflamed, by weeping,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by grief"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sorrow;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hot"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its tears."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","S","MA","L","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n19244","headword_ar":"سَخْنٌ","root":"sxn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxonapN","text_ar":"سُخْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  [The signification of “ calor aquæ aliarumve rerum, ” assigned to it by Freytag as on the authority of J, is a mistake, probably occasioned by a fault in his copy of the S.]"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n19245","headword_ar":"سُخْنٌ","root":"sxn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of 1 [q. v.]. (MA, L, K.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"warm;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, PS;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAr~N","text_ar":"حَارٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, MA, Mgh, L, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAridN","text_ar":"بَارِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (JK, L;) an epithet applied to water, (JK, MA, Mgh, L,) &c.; (Msb;) as is also (in the same sense, JK, MA, Mgh, L) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxiynN","text_ar":"سَخِينٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, S, MA, Mgh, L, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAxinN","text_ar":"سَاخِنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musoxanN","text_ar":"مُسْخَنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxiynN","text_ar":"سَخِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muboramN","text_ar":"مُبْرَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariymN","text_ar":"بَرِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c., (IAar, S, L,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musax~anN","text_ar":"مُسَخَّنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [which is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musoxanN","text_ar":"مُسْخَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"warmed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEaZ~amN","text_ar":"مُعَظَّمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in measure], (K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"six~iynN","text_ar":"سِخِّينٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxaAxiynN","text_ar":"سُخَاخِينٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the only instance of the measure, (S, L, K, [which measure is said in the S to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEaAEiylN","text_ar":"فُعَاعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but in the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEaAliylN","text_ar":"فُعَالِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) and which is also applied to food; (L;) syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAr~N","text_ar":"حَارٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L, K:) or, accord. to AA, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxiynN","text_ar":"سَخِينٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to water, means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"neither hot nor cold;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxiymN","text_ar":"سَخِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN suxonN","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ سُخْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAxinN","text_ar":"سَاخِنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxonaAnN","text_ar":"سَخْنَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxanaAnN","text_ar":"سَخَنَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (accord. to different copies of the S,) or both these, (K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxonaAnN","text_ar":"سُخْنَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K, * [in the CK and in my MS. copy of the K written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxonaAnu","text_ar":"سُخْنَانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is incorrect, and in like manner"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxonaAnN","text_ar":"سَخْنَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is there written ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxonaAnu","text_ar":"سَخْنَانُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this, as well as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxonaAnN","text_ar":"سَخْنَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", may be correct, for it appears that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxonaAn","text_ar":"سَخْنَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"has"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxonaA='u","text_ar":"سَخْنَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"for its fem. as well as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxonaAnapN","text_ar":"سَخْنَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxaAxiynN","text_ar":"سُخَاخِينٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same, [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"warm, day,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or, accord. to IAar, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN suxaAxiynN","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ سُخَاخِينٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a day that is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so hot as to be"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurtful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"painful:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN suxonapN","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ سُخْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAxinapN","text_ar":"سَاخِنَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxonaAnapN","text_ar":"سَخْنَانَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxanaAnapN","text_ar":"سَخَنَانَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, accord. to different copies,) or both, (K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxonaAnapN","text_ar":"سُخْنَانَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"warm, night,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN saxanaAnN","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ سَخَنَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a day intensely hot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN saxonaA='u","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ سَخْنَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the latter word being fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxonaAnu","text_ar":"سَخْنَانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sultry night,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intensely hot so that it takes away the breath:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK:) and it is said in a trad. of Mo'áwiyeh Ibn-Kurrah, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ar~u Al$~itaA='i Als~axiynu","text_ar":"شَرُّ الشِّتَا=ءِ السَّخِينُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The worst of winter is"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the hot in which is no cold;"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the “ Ghareeb ” of El- Harbee, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~uxayoxiynu","text_ar":"السُّخَيْخِينُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", expl. as meaning the same, but this is probably a mistranscription. (L.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","MA","Mgh","L","S","Msb","K","IAar"]},{"entry_id":"n19246","headword_ar":"سَخَنٌ","root":"sxn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of 1 [q. v., last sentence]. See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxonapN","text_ar":"سُخْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"page_break","n":1327}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}